  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Iron Rebellion is a VR multiplayer sci-fi mech shooter SIM that puts you in the pilot’s seat. Customize your mech, control every system from inside the cockpit, and face other players in fast-paced, tactical PvP battles.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>True VR Mech Pilot Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built exclusively for VR, Iron Rebellion delivers a fully physical mech combat experience where every switch, lever, and system is under your control.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical 8v8 PvP Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form elite 8v8 squads to dominate the fight in multiple game modes. Victory depends on teamwork and smart decision-making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/2a421ac4f554fc4211aeff53e41305cf.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/2a421ac4f554fc4211aeff53e41305cf.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/2a421ac4f554fc4211aeff53e41305cf.mp4?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deep Mech Loadout Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six distinct mech classes, fine-tune your mech using an extensive augment and loadout system, and customize your mech’s appearance. Adaptation is key to survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Expanding Cross-Platform Universe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Iron Rebellion supports PCVR and standalone Quest with <strong>a cross-platform multiplayer experience</strong>. With an engaged community and active ongoing development, Iron Rebellion is evolving beyond individual matches into an ongoing war. PvE launching in 2026.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d9d5fe8faea15e8e846ab5ac9f923804.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d9d5fe8faea15e8e846ab5ac9f923804.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d9d5fe8faea15e8e846ab5ac9f923804.mp4?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/79d49ed4042d9ede0965539a6e2f02e6.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/79d49ed4042d9ede0965539a6e2f02e6.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/79d49ed4042d9ede0965539a6e2f02e6.mp4?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d053d4b57e6e9a743f071445997401ee.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d053d4b57e6e9a743f071445997401ee.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d053d4b57e6e9a743f071445997401ee.mp4?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Iron Rebellion is a VR multiplayer sci-fi mech shooter SIM that puts you in the pilot’s seat. Customize your mech, control every system from inside the cockpit, and face other players in fast-paced, tactical PvP battles.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>True VR Mech Pilot Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built exclusively for VR, Iron Rebellion delivers a fully physical mech combat experience where every switch, lever, and system is under your control.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical 8v8 PvP Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form elite 8v8 squads to dominate the fight in multiple game modes. Victory depends on teamwork and smart decision-making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/2a421ac4f554fc4211aeff53e41305cf.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/2a421ac4f554fc4211aeff53e41305cf.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/2a421ac4f554fc4211aeff53e41305cf.mp4?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deep Mech Loadout Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six distinct mech classes, fine-tune your mech using an extensive augment and loadout system, and customize your mech’s appearance. Adaptation is key to survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Expanding Cross-Platform Universe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Iron Rebellion supports PCVR and standalone Quest with <strong>a cross-platform multiplayer experience</strong>. With an engaged community and active ongoing development, Iron Rebellion is evolving beyond individual matches into an ongoing war. PvE launching in 2026.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d9d5fe8faea15e8e846ab5ac9f923804.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d9d5fe8faea15e8e846ab5ac9f923804.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d9d5fe8faea15e8e846ab5ac9f923804.mp4?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/79d49ed4042d9ede0965539a6e2f02e6.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/79d49ed4042d9ede0965539a6e2f02e6.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/79d49ed4042d9ede0965539a6e2f02e6.mp4?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d053d4b57e6e9a743f071445997401ee.poster.avif?t=1773947997\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/d053d4b57e6e9a743f071445997401ee.webm?t=1773947997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1192900/extras/